# Usage:
#
# Specify either of the following:
#
# i) a single value (used uniformly across all forced words); e.g.,
#
# **+
#
#
# ii) one value per forced dimension (used uniformly across all the corresponding forced words); e.g.,
#
# *-
# *-
# *+
#
#
# iii) one value per forced word; e.g.,
#
# + + - +
# -
# - +

**+
